data: {"text": "**"}

event: answer_delta
data: {"text": "In canon:** Anakin Skywalker was trained by **Qui-Gon Jinn** (his first"}

event: answer_delta
data: {"text": " Jedi mentor), then **Obi-Wan Kenobi** (who took"}

event: answer_delta
data: {"text": " him as his Padawan after Qui-Gon's death), **Yoda** (as a member of the J"}

event: answer_delta
data: {"text": "edi Order/High Council training), and later **Darth Sidious** ("}

event: answer_delta
data: {"text": "Palpatine), who trained him in the ways of the Sith.\n\n**In Legends:** Anakin was trained by **Qui-Gon Jinn**"}

event: answer_delta
data: {"text": ", **Obi-Wan Kenobi**, **Ki-Adi-Mundi**, and **Palpatine** (as his Sith Master)."}

